secretly planning to thrash me.

317
00:25:06.557 --> 00:25:08.763
No. sir. You are like God to us.

318
00:25:09.016 --> 00:25:11.152
Then why don't you all
give aarti to me everyday?

319
00:25:12.307 --> 00:25:13.141
Kaachi!

320
