- Can't you hear me? Get out from here.
- It'll not be more than two minutes.

1745
02:10:42.348 --> 02:10:43.806
- Go...
- It is very important matter.

1746
02:10:44.014 --> 02:10:45.014
- [indistinct chatter]
- Karthik...

1747
